The '''slitherhorn''', also called the '''traz''', was a [[Music/Legends|musical]] instrument common among [[Jizz/Legends|jizz]] bands during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. It was similar in appearance to the [[Kloo horn/Legends|kloo horn]], though smaller in size. [[Rodian/Legends|Rodian]] musician [[Doda Bodonawieedo/Legends|Doda Bodonawieedo]] played the slitherhorn in the [[Max Rebo Band/Legends|Max Rebo Band]].

